1.1.1.1
log
@pgpool-II is a middleware that sits between PostgreSQL servers and a
PostgreSQL database client. It provides the following features:

+ Connection Pooling
+ Replication
+ Load Balance
+ Limiting Exceeding Connections
+ Parallel Query

with tweaks from ajacoutot@@, thanks.

